== Borea Mornna Khatir Magnnem ==
'''Prayer for Happy Death''' 

Khursar marlelea Kakutsara [[Jezu]], Mhojea mornnacho ugddas kor. 

Oti-konvallia [[Jezu]]chea kallza, bhalean ugtem kelelea mhojea 

jivitache nimmnne ghoddier mhaka rakh. Mhoje khatir [[Jezu]]chea kallzantsun 

vhanvlelea Rogta ani Udka, ogonit kakutiche zhori, [[Jezu]] Tum mhoje khatir 

tujea mornanna gahann zaloi, mhojea mornnachea vellar, Tuzo rag pois kor. 



'''''Amen''''' 





